## Operator-side: how to read the new logs

After this lands, every silent failure will print to the devtools console with a `[module/function]` prefix. To monitor in production:

- Open devtools on the extension's service worker (chrome://extensions → "service worker" link)
- Open devtools on the UI page
- Open devtools on the offscreen document (chrome://extensions → "offscreen" link, if available)
- Filter by `[` prefix or specific module name when investigating a report

Errors will not block the pipeline. They surface so you can investigate.